Package org.domainobject.orm.map

Contains classes concerned with mapping class and field names to table and column names.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMappingAlgorithm
    Interface specifying methods for mapping class names to table names and field names to column names.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMappingAlgorithm
    Default implementation used for IMappingAlgorithm.
    LowerCaseMappingAlgorithm
    Maps class names and field names to lowercase table names and column names, using the underscore character to separate the name parts.
    NoOpMappingAlgorithm
    Maps class names and fields names as-is to table names and column names.
    UpperCaseMappingAlgorithm
    Maps class names and field names to uppercase table names and column names, using the underscore character to separate the name parts.

Package org.domainobject.orm.map Description

Contains classes concerned with mapping class and field names to table and column names.
